==敘利亞內戰==
{{main|馬盧納戰鬥}}

2013年9月，[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]與敘政府軍在馬盧拉交戰。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-23986076 | work=BBC News | title=Syria rebels withdraw from ancient Christian town of Maaloula | date=September 6, 2013 | accessdate=2016-04-05 | archive-date=2019-04-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415172056/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-23986076 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年10月21日，反政府武裝攻佔馬盧拉。<ref name="barnabasfund.org">{{cite web |url=http://barnabasfund.org/UK/Islamists-besiege-two-Christian-villages-in-Syria-13-people-killed.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207163944/http://barnabasfund.org/UK/Islamists-besiege-two-Christian-villages-in-Syria-13-people-killed.html |archivedate=2013-12-07 }}</ref>10月28日被政府軍收復。<ref name="barnabasfund.org"/>

努斯拉陣線於2013年12月3日再度攻佔馬盧拉。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/articles/527153/20131203/syria-abducted-nuns-islamist-rebels-maaloula-christians.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-04-05 |archive-date=2013-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212134646/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/articles/527153/20131203/syria-abducted-nuns-islamist-rebels-maaloula-christians.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年4月14日，敘軍在[[真主黨|真主黨]]的幫助下收復馬盧拉。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.yahoo.com/syria-army-retakes-christian-town-maalula-090238420.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-04-05 |archive-date=2014-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429050851/http://news.yahoo.com/syria-army-retakes-christian-town-maalula-090238420.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-27025022|title=BBC News - Syria rebels driven from Christian town of Maaloula|work=BBC News|accessdate=25 October 2014|archive-date=2017-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171026053701/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-27025022|dead-url=no}}</ref>

